title: Ep. - 236 - BACHELOR FINALE REVIEW NEXT IN FASHION REVIEW
description:
Worst Ever Podcast co-hosts and Alaa Khaled and Christine Laykin review Next in Fashion on Netflix, a series where eighteen designers compete in rounds based on design trends and styles that influence what people wear worldwide. The contestants are all professionals who have been dressing celebrities and working with major fashion houses. The winner receives USD$250,000 and can debut a collection with Net-a-Porter, a luxury fashion retailer. 

 

Stacey McGunnigle, co-host of The Regulars Podcast, helps Kate review the The Bachelor’s two-part and Love is Blind finales.
